# Files/folders that do NOT need a matching test file.
#
# Adding an entry here is a HUMAN decision: the exempt-guard gate BLOCKS any
# commit that adds a line unless it is landed with ALLOW_EXEMPT=1. An agent
# cannot exempt itself out of writing a test. Keep this list short — prefer
# writing the test.
#
# Format: repo-relative path; a trailing "/" means "this folder and everything under it".

fly.py       # plotting entrypoint — no meaningful unit test
scripts/     # the gate + orchestration tooling itself
